# 5. Relationships

```text
Tenant
    │
    │ 1
    ▼
TenantWorkspace
```

A Tenant owns many TenantWorkspaces.

A TenantWorkspace belongs to exactly one Tenant.

---

# 6. Business Rules

* Tenant must exist.
* WorkspaceCode is unique within the owning Tenant.
* WorkspaceName is unique within the owning Tenant.
* WorkspaceCode is immutable.
* Archived workspaces cannot be modified.
* Workspaces cannot move between Tenants.
* Workspaces cannot be hard deleted.

